Flow Charts

Macro flow chart
	more general
	gets the idea across

Micro flowchart
	more detailed
	trapezoin = io
	diamonds = conditions
	rectangle = processing

EOF vs Sentinal


Libraries in UNIX
	static library
		functions export with program
		multiple copies
	shared library
		lists all the references required
		on runtime loads/links the library functions at start
	dynamic link library (shared)
		lists needed library functions
		loads function when it is called
		might get destroyed between function calls
Reentrant code
	unique data sections
	shared code sections
	